{"tid":1747364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"借位出 - 「有圖」我地仲有100個手足係POLY","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T10:42:40.000Z","uid":324007,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fcdf169e378bda69fd803a245d33b0d200127335","tid":1747364,"uid":324007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"希望大家除咗區選，記得我哋仲有手足係poly <br />\n<br />\n借位出 - 「有圖」我地仲有100個手足係POLY<br />\n<br />\n首先，好多謝大家關心，今日見到咁多人陪我地食生命面包真心感動，我地收到曬！講到明和勇不分，雖然攻唔返入嚟poly，但係我地守係到嘅一早做好曬心理準備，大家唔好再送頭。<br />\n<br />\n講返POLY現況，CCTVB講30位手足係流料，我地起碼有100位手足係到！係，衛生環境的確係差，好多手足都係帶傷，每晚都訓唔到，好攰好想知幾時會完。但係我地想同POPO講：你咁樣我地係唔會驚嫁!!! Mon po狗我知你睇到，你哋繼續係出面守門口呃OT，留返你啲OT海底撈啦，我地慢慢同你玩!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASGGhgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASGGhgr.jpg&h=928795f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mW2NXgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmW2NXgr.jpg&h=1af85ccd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67cd56eec4cef447749bbb47d821e8fecc9f5f1e","tid":1747364,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7a75ba62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推行動post拉！連登有邊個唔去投票！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ba069c1fd6f6121ca998c41d17ecb3e13e22daf","tid":1747364,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"撐住呀 岀面好多人都未放棄嫁"},{"pid":"f8bff6343a8a47f72dfd3d3964489e0465161324","tid":1747364,"uid":36378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"頂住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd8fce32ae4522a9bcd180650f3df47aa6c8e5","tid":1747364,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"我地有咩可以幫到手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5096d8078f141d5b7ab1aedfccd36a4ac3626650","tid":1747364,"uid":55309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:01:38.000Z","msg":"頂住啊<br />\n泰國少年足球隊全部成員都出到黎<br />\n你地一樣得<br />\n支持你地<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\"